{"type": "article", "id": 27179, "title": "可以做花器的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-23T06:53:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144037ThiZ3LgM2NW8Bz4D.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>台灯除了照明还能用来做什么？SHare Studios 的设计师 Stephanie Hare 大胆地将玻璃器皿作为底座，搭配手工制作的纸质灯罩，推出了一系列极简风格的灯具。如果不用做花器，只是单纯放上一束花或是一些绿叶也能使人眼前一亮。这里是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/SHareStudios\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">购买链接</a>，价格根据大小从 150 到 250 美元不等。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144035w2B9kPrZDI8Lh7ub.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144035UEoQisTju2Rfvnek.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66990291\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021440369k20SgRQIfeaz74W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021440364AEDHeWkw8aBo7Fc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}